case_id: enclosure-hollow-box
possible: partial
awkwardness: high
pain_points[2]:
  - "Shelling is emulated by manually sizing and offsetting an inner box."
  - "Wall thickness intent is implicit and easy to break with edits."
proposed_features[2]:
  - "Shell feature with wall thickness and open-face options."
  - "Offset-body operation with topology-aware validation."
reviewer_verdict: "Expressed with primitive subtraction, but true enclosure shell semantics are missing."
